     I                                       85  86 SHN3
     I                                       87  91 MHN1
     I                                       92  96 MHN2
     I                                       97 101 MHN3
     I                                      102 106 MHN4
     I                                      107 107 TKR1
     I                                      108 109 TKR2
     I                                      110 111 TKR3
     I                                      112 112 TKR4
     I                                      113 1170SSYS
